snippet.title: War Inc. Battlezone - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
"War Inc. Battlezone" delivers a premium online game experience in a F2P package, as an addictive 3rd-person shooter punctuated by high production value and a rich, frequently updated set of game features.

For more information on War Inc. Battlezone and the latest in gaming news, check out: http://www.gamefront.com

Download this trailer at: http://www.gamefront.com/files/20568493/WAR_Trl_Final_PlayFreeOnly.wmv
